# Project docs lifecycle

- Material change to `docs/`, `AGENTS.md`, onboarding, or user-facing copy → update `docs/docs-map.json` per `docs/docs-map-schema.md`.
- Invoke `/maintain-project-docs` or follow its checklist when map entries are stale or missing.
- change/build/fix touching docs → include Docs Impact Record (`.cursor/skills/autonomous-task/contracts.md`).
- Validate: `scripts/validate-project-docs.ps1` (exit 0) before claiming doc work done.
